                <mxCell id="8" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Gap Analysis&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;We want to find out what we don&#39;t know.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;line-height: 100%;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Did we lose any information in the process from the system logs going to spunk, to us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;were there indicators that were seen in the system data but not in Treat Connect&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
