                <mxCell id="31" value="&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;b&gt;Identify key identifier&lt;/b&gt;: IP Address&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;will be the unqiue identifier to match&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;records between sys data and threat connect data&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="42" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry width="290" height="60" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="32" value="Categorize Data:&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;Matched - Data present in both sys and threat connect&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Mismatched - Data present in both sys and threat connect but with discrepencies&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Missing - Data present in sys but not in threat connect&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="42" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry y="60" width="450" height="70" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="36" value="Matches - records that exist in both locations and meet the comparison&lt;div&gt;Mismatches - records that exist in both locations but differ in some values&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Missing Data - records that exist in sys logs but are not found&amp;nbsp; in threat connect&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="42" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry y="175" width="440" height="70" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="38" value="If you find a Match:&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Validate - Double check the match to ensure accuracy&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- No Action Needed - If the match is correct, no further action is required.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Optional - Log the match for reporting purposes&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;If you find a Mismatch:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Investigate - Identify if theres a cause for the decrepency&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Resolve if possible&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;If data is missing:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- determine why the data is missing&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- could potentially filter in missing data&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- be sure that insertion process maintains data integrity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="42" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry y="275" width="440" height="210" as="geometry"/>
